peeweep's overlay

How to use:

1. layman:
  sudo su
  echo 'app-portage/layman sync-plugin-portage git' > /etc/portage/package.use/layman
  emerge --ask --quiet app-portage/layman
  layman -o https://codeberg.org/peeweep/gentoo-overlay/raw/branch/master/layman.xml -f -a peeweep
  echo '*/*::peeweep ~amd64' > /etc/portage/package.accept_keywords/peeweep

2. custom repos.conf:

  sudo su
  wget https://codeberg.org/peeweep/gentoo-overlay/raw/branch/master/peeweep-overlay.conf -O /etc/portage/repos.conf/peeweep-overlay.conf
  emerge --sync
  echo '*/*::peeweep ~amd64' > /etc/portage/package.accept_keywords/peeweep
